'From Squeak2.9alpha of 12 June 2000 [latest update: #3351] on 1 February 2001 at 8:58:34 pm'!"Change Set:		TwoWayLayoutDate:			1 February 2001Author:			Andreas RaabAt the request of Dan I., fixes a horrendous waste in layout of new tiles during insertion."!!TwoWayScrollPane methodsFor: 'layout' stamp: 'ar 2/1/2001 17:00'!doLayoutIn: layoutBounds	"layout has changed. update scroll deltas or whatever else"	self valueOfProperty: #maxAutoFitSize ifPresentDo:		[:maxFitSize |		self fitContentsUpTo: maxFitSize.		^super doLayoutIn: layoutBounds].	scroller ifNotNil: [self setScrollDeltas].	super doLayoutIn: layoutBounds.! !TwoWayScrollPane removeSelector: #layoutChanged!!TwoWayScrollPane reorganize!('initialization' initialize)('access' colorForInsets scroller wantsSlot)('geometry' containsPoint: extent: fitContentsUpTo: leftoverScrollRange resizeScrollBar resizeScroller scrollBarFills: scrollBy: scrollIntoView:extra: setScrollDeltas totalScrollRange)('retractable scroll bar' hideOrShowScrollBar hideOrShowScrollBar:forRange: mouseEnter: mouseLeave:)('pane events' handlesMouseDown: handlesMouseOver: keyStroke: mouseDown: mouseMove: mouseUp: rejectsEvent:)('scroll bar events' scrollBarMenuButtonPressed: shiftedYellowButtonActivity unshiftedYellowButtonActivity xScrollBarMenuButtonPressed: xScrollBarValue: yScrollBarMenuButtonPressed: yScrollBarValue: yellowButtonActivity:)('menu' addCustomMenuItems:hand: getMenu: leftOrRight menuTitleSelector: retractableOrNot scrollBarOnLeft:)('layout' doLayoutIn:)!